author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of The Jayhawks featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited The Current studio back in 2016.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 Quiet Corners & Empty Spaces
00:03:11 Comeback Kids
00:06:59 Lover of the Sun
00:10:17 Leaving the Monsters Behind

Musicians
Gary Louris — vocals, guitar
Marc Perlman — bass
Tim O’Reagan — drums, vocals
Karen Grotberg — keyboard, piano, vocals
Chet Lysters — guitar, vocals

Credits
Engineer – Michael DeMark
Producer – Andrea Swensson
Visuals  – Nate Ryan
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.
